rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0001
rows.name:
I got demoted for letting Iira get
away.

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0002
rows.name:
And now? Now I'm back to the old
garrison patrol.

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But I've got to say, it's a fair sight
better than being bossed around
by a lousy boss...

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0004
rows.name:
My salary took a hefty blow, but really
this suits me just fine. I can get by.

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Wh-what's Special Inquisitor Meleph
doing here in Trigo...?!

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0006
rows.name:
O-oh, forgive me! Please, forget
I said anything!

rows.label: tlk006701_04_msg0007
rows.name:
I, Pax, will humbly carry out my
duty as is expected of my station!
